**Role:** Senior Frontend Engineer & UI/UX Designer
**Tech Stack:** React, Tailwind CSS, Lucide React Icons.
**Design Reference:** Clean B2B SaaS style (similar to Amplitude/Stripe).
**Objective:** Create a high-conversion landing page ensuring the "Section 5" cards match exactly the reference image style (image on top, clean white card, blue link at bottom).

---

### üé® GLOBAL VISUAL GUIDELINES
1.  **Typography:** Use a modern Sans-Serif font (Inter or system-ui).
    * **Headings:** Dark Slate (`text-slate-900`), Bold/Extrabold, tight tracking (`tracking-tight`).
    * **Body:** Medium Slate (`text-slate-600`), relaxed line-height (`leading-relaxed`).
2.  **Color Palette:**
    * **Primary Brand:** Royal Blue (`bg-blue-600`, `text-blue-600`, `hover:bg-blue-700`).
    * **Backgrounds:** Clean White (`bg-white`) alternating with Light Gray/Blueish (`bg-slate-50` or `bg-blue-50/30`).
    * **Borders:** Subtle (`border-slate-200`).
3.  **Spacing:** Generous whitespace between sections (`py-20` or `py-24`).

